# Thrives Archivers

An educational platform to help students excel in Natural Sciences.

## 🔧 Features
- Full-page frontend in HTML
- Backend using Express.js and file storage
- Supports login/signup with bcrypt password hashing

## 🛠️ Installation
```bash
npm install
npm start
```

## 🌐 Endpoints
- `POST /api/signup`
- `POST /api/login`
- `GET /api/status`
